# Project Overview

This is a Next.js TypeScript project with the following key directories:

- `app/`: Contains Next.js app router pages and layouts
- `components/`: Reusable React components
- `actions/`: Server actions for handling data mutations
- `utils/`: Utility functions and helpers
- `lib/`: Core library code and configurations
- `hooks/`: Custom React hooks
- `prisma/`: Database schema and Prisma configurations

Key configuration files:
- [next.config.ts](mdc:next.config.ts): Next.js configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json): TypeScript configuration
- [package.json](mdc:package.json): Project dependencies and scripts
- [docker-compose.yml](mdc:docker-compose.yml): Docker configuration
